cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM. 

The paper addresses the problem of retrieving a specific moment from an untrimmed video by a query sentence, which involves natural language processing and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a Temporal Adjacent Network (2D-TAN) for moment localization, which involves machine learning and deep learning techniques. Therefore, the paper may also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
